NAME
       ldns_zone_rr_count - get ldns_zone size

SYNOPSIS
       #include <stdint.h>
       #include <stdbool.h>

       #include <ldns/ldns.h>

       size_t ldns_zone_rr_count(const ldns_zone *z);

DESCRIPTION
       ldns_zone_rr_count() Returns the number of resource records in the zone, NOT counting the SOA record
              z: the zone to read from
              Returns the number of rr's in the zone

